  "abstract": "Striga , the parasitic weed, has long been recognized as serious\r\nProblem on sorghum in India and many African countries. In India, it is\r\nKnown to occur in many parts causing severe damage to the sorghum crop.\r\nIt is posing a serious threat to the cultivation of high yielding sorghum\r\nhybrids in some areas as they were found to be more susceptible to the pest.\r\nIn view of this, there is now a greater awareness of the....................\r\n",
